body:
{"operationName":"stackProfile","variables":{"id":"yahoo/yahoo"},"query":"query stackProfile($id: String!) {
  stackProfile(identifier: $id) {
    id
    slug
    name
    path
    imageUrl
    viewCount
    amIOwner
    toolsAvatars
    embedUrl
    stackMatchPercentage
    ad {
      imageUrl
      targetUrl
      text
      title
      sponsorFeatured
      sponsorToolId
      ctaText
      __typename
    }
    strengthMeter {
      dismissed
      percentComplete
      items {
        completed
        slug
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    permissions {
      edit
      delete
      __typename
    }
    services {
      id
      name
      slug
      title
      imageUrl
      following
      votes
      fans
      stacks
      canonicalUrl
      layer {
        slug
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    owner {
      ... on Company {
        id
        imageUrl
        name
        slug
        path
        verified
        amIOwner
        following
        owners {
          id
          __typename
        }
        team(first: 100) {
          count
          edges {
            node {
              id
              displayName
              username
              imageUrl
              title
              popularity
              path
              stacksCount
              favoritesCount
              votesCount
              __typename
            }
            __typename
          }
          __typename
        }
        jobs(first: 4) {
          count
          edges {
            node {
              id
              url
              title
              location
              services {
                id
                name
                slug
                title
                verified
                imageUrl
                path
                votes
                fans
                stacks
                __typename
              }
              __typename
            }
            __typename
          }
          __typename
        }
        __typename
      }
      ... on User {
        id
        imageUrl
        displayName
        title
        username
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
"}
